text: A compound of octahedra may be: *Compound of two octahedra *Compound of three octahedra ** Also Compound of three triangular antiprisms *Compound of four octahedra ** More generally, Compound of four octahedra with rotational freedom *Compound of five octahedra *Compound of eight octahedra with rotational freedom *Compound of ten octahedra *Compound of twenty octahedra **More generally, Compound of twenty octahedra with rotational freedom Category:Polyhedral compounds
title: Compound of octahedra
